(260, 'Mahmoud Ayman', 'Mahmoud Ayman', 'ma3538463@gmail.com', '$2y$10$QzomndDlngHgi.gJrIAdeeM28wLh/dm2Z/hoqpunT7Dsa/YdI.8Sq', '01276593927', '00000000', 'cairo', 'Web Developer', NULL, NULL, 'The scene is total chaos: a woman and all her purse\'s contents in middair as she trips over a child\'s toy, a man hastily trying to gather his spilled laundry, a screaming child weaving through the crowd. Somewhere, in the midst of it all, is the person you\'ve been looking for: wearing a red and white striped shirt, black rimmed glasses and a lopsided cap. There he is! There\'s Waldo.\r\nMany of us have fond memories of Waldo. But while he looms large in our imagination, our childhood searches for Waldo typically stayed pretty small – Waldo is a tiny person in the middle of lots of other tiny things.', '8df4429cbaa3fa50b767fd615b020202.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'https://twitter.com/Mahmoud17272776?t=2FpfjATUp_vilBdrG-C_Bg&s=35', 'https://twitter.com/Mahmoud17272776?t=2FpfjATUp_vilBdrG-C_Bg&s=35', 'https://www.instagram.com/mahmod.ayman99/', NULL, 'https://www.instagram.com/mahmod.ayman99/', '2022-08-25 15:00:19', 4, 0, NULL, NULL, 'Africa/Cairo', '2022-08-25 15:00:19', '2023-04-02 20:23:06', '2023-04-02 20:23:06', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
