(702, NULL, 'Ibrahim ismail ismail', 'ibrahim.ismail.c@gmail.com', '$2y$10$utkFxlR3kMJe/OQfsToy4ujKyoadXFa4dg5E5lfxS7zmmWGUrERDm', '01111422304', '29810010105171', 'Maadi', 'lawyer', '24', '2023-04-25', 'Ibrahim is a dedicated lawyer who has always had a passion for giving back to his community. He began volunteering during his school years and continued to do so throughout his university studies. It was this commitment to service that led him to join our non-profit organization.\r\nWith a strong belief in the power of doing what you love, Ibrahim brings a unique perspective to our team. He understands that when you can do what you do best and be happy, you are further along in life than most people. This philosophy drives him to work tirelessly on behalf of our organization and the individuals we serve.\r\nIn addition to his legal work, Ibrahim is also an active volunteer within our organization. He is always willing to lend a helping hand wherever it is needed, whether it\'s organizing events or working.\r\nWe are proud to have Ibrahim as part of our team and grateful for his unwavering commitment to making a difference in the lives of others.', '5fd364f0fe96b151ca62b8c91b64fc20.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'https://www.facebook.com/juge.Ibrahim', NULL, 'https://www.linkedin.com/in/ibrahim-ismail1', NULL, 'https://www.linkedin.com/in/ibrahim-ismail1', '2023-04-15 15:33:02', 6, 0, NULL, NULL, 'Africa/Cairo', '2023-04-15 15:32:38', '2023-04-25 14:01:20', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
