(880, 'Ahmed Mohamed Mohamed Gad Hoter', 'Ahmed Mohamed Mohamed Gad Hoter', 'ahmedgad444444gad@gmail.com', '$2y$10$5TOtvgQRCe4InQn8Srz9QunUj4xwsG7gHCIj4CGuTUj.igMwmIUwy', '01021888533', '29803061800438', 'Abis, El Raml 2, Alexandria', 'HR Recruiter', '26', '1998-03-06', 'Human Resources professional successful working in fast-paced changing environments demanding strong interpersonal, time management, and technical skills with a successful record of building and improving processes, with a demonstrated history of working in the non-profit organization management industry, Skilled in Negotiation, Communication, Public Speaking, Time Management, and Teamwork.\r\nI worked on representing the Arab Republic of Egypt within the BRICS grouping and was the chairman of the session within the grouping  under the auspices of Prime Minister Dr. Mostafa Madbouly , In the period from February 19 to March 1 inside the Engineering Authority of the armed forces in the presence of the ambassador of India, Russia, China, South Africa, Brazil, representatives of the United Arab Emirates and Saudi Arabia, the Egyptian Minister of youth and sports, the Assistant Minister of foreign affairs of Egypt , Assistant Minister of planning and international cooperation and dean of the Faculty of Economics and Political Science, Future University , The media spokesman for President Abdel Fattah al-Sisi\'s election campaign , Assistant to the head of the support and decision-making center of the Council of ministers , The model came up with many important recommendations, amid the optimism of the members of the simulation model and their confidence in the future of the BRICS countries and their ability to overcome challenges and achieve progress and prosperity for the peoples of those countries.', '547f5941a79d5d87be9a8ec80583f789.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'https://www.facebook.com/AhmedHoter123?mibextid=ZbWKwL', 'https://x.com/gad_hoter?t=JKlrLHPjs_AK7R9UL8fhuw&s=09', 'https://www.instagram.com/ahmedhoter123?igsh=MXE4MzJoNm9sM291ZA==', NULL, 'https://www.linkedin.com/in/ahmed-hoter123', '2024-03-12 21:19:07', 6, 0, NULL, NULL, 'Africa/Cairo', '2024-03-12 20:40:42', '2024-03-20 15:11:54', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
