 and Sports \r\n- Share the possibility of Egypt\'s love for athletes \r\n- Participate in a ceremony honoring the successful icons of Egyptian women under the name She deserves. \r\n\r\nCapacity: \r\n- General leadership of many people Organizing conferences and seminars \r\n- The ability to handle problems and solve them \r\n\r\n\r\nCertificates: \r\n- Certificate from Habiba Al Khair Association \r\n- Certificate from Noor Al-Sama Association \r\n- Certificate of appreciation for participating in organizing the law centers of the Ministry of Youth and Sports in universities \r\n\r\nLanguage \r\n- Arabic: Native. \r\n- English: Good. \r\n- French: Good. \r\n\r\nPersonal Data:\r\nDate of Birth: 09-03-1997 \r\nNationality: Egyptian \r\nMarital Status: Single \r\nMilitary Status: Exempted.', '71393d1f3fb29130b766186f78a95cb0.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'https://www.facebook.com/profile.php?id=100006750372631&mibextid=ZbWKwL', 'https://www.facebook.com/profile.php?id=100006750372631&mibextid=ZbWKwL', 'https://www.facebook.com/profile.php?id=100006750372631&mibextid=ZbWKwL', NULL, 'https://www.facebook.com/profile.php?id=100006750372631&mibextid=ZbWKwL', '2024-03-15 20:06:48', 6, 0, NULL, NULL, 'Africa/Cairo', '2024-03-15 19:48:20', '2024-03-20 15:15:23', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
